csDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ues1665702645905.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ues1665702645905.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ues1665702645905.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ues1665702645905\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the default video attributes for fields.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ues1665702645905__topic_d139943e1_d139944e1_d139945e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ues1665702645905__p_d139946e1_d139947e1_d139948e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DEF_VIDEO</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">Attribute</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">AttributeN</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>...}</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ues1665702645905__p_d139949e1_d139950e1_d139951e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$DEF_VIDEO = (BRI,UND)</code>\n</p>\n</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ues1665702645905__section_zcl_d1p_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d935080e84\"> Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ues1665702645905__p_d139955e1_d139956e1_d139957e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Attribute</var>—video attribute code. When combining video attributes, you can\n        enclose them in parentheses.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Video Attribute Codes</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\"> Attribute Code </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">BLI</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\"> Blinking </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">BOR</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\"> Border </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">BRI</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\"> Bright </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HLT</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\">Use system highlight color. <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ues1665702645905__d5999e85\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This attribute always takes precedence over other video attributes that may be specified.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">INV</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\"> Inverse </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UND</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\"> Underline </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">COL=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16616e1_d16617e1_d16618e1__entry__2\"> Set color to color code\n\t\t\t\t <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var>, the sum of the color numbers for foreground and background. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ues1665702645905__section_tnn_f1p_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d935080e215\"> Defaults </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ues1665702645905__table_d16646e1_d16647e1_d16648e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> client assignment files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> [SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ues1665702645905__section_trt_f1p_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d935080e261\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ues1665702645905__p_d139970e1_d139971e1_d139972e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DEF_VIDEO</span> sets the default video\n        attributes for all fields in forms. In addition, it sets the value of the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">DEF</code> parameter used with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvideo</span> and\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fieldvideo</span> ProcScript instructions.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ues1665702645905__note_wgp_j1p_bwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> You cannot test or change the value of\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DEF_VIDEO</span> in ProcScript.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ues1665702645905__section_fst_j1p_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d935080e288\">Example: $DEF_VIDEO</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ues1665702645905__p_d139976e1_d139977e1_d139978e1\">To make fields appear by default with white letters on\n        a blue background, determine the color number by adding 56 (white foreground) and 1 (blue\n        background):</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ues1665702645905__pre_e1t_v1p_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$DEF_VIDEO COL=57</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ues1665702645905__p_d139979e1_d139980e1_d139981e1\">To make fields appear by default in high intensity and\n        underlined, use the following assignment:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ues1665702645905__pre_f1t_v1p_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$DEF_VIDEO BRI,UND</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsj1665702873847.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Video Attributes</a><p>Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdn1718900940684.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldvideo</a><p>Return or set the video attributes of the specified field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$DEF_VIDEO Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the default video attributes for fields. $DEF_VIDEO { = } Attribute { , AttributeN , ...} Example: $DEF_VIDEO = (BRI,UND) Arguments Attribute —video attribute code. When combining video attributes, you can enclose them in parentheses. Table 1. Video Attribute Codes Attribute Code Description BLI Blinking BOR Border BRI Bright HLT Use system highlight color. Note: This attribute always takes precedence over other video attributes that may be specified. INV Inverse UND Underline COL= n Set color to color code n , the sum of the color numbers for foreground and background. Defaults Assignment file: client assignment files Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $DEF_VIDEO sets the default video attributes for all fields in forms. In addition, it sets the value of the DEF parameter used with the $fieldvideo and fieldvideo ProcScript instructions. Note: You cannot test or change the value of $DEF_VIDEO in ProcScript. Example: $DEF_VIDEO To make fields appear by default with white letters on a blue background, determine the color number by adding 56 (white foreground) and 1 (blue background): $DEF_VIDEO COL=57 Copy To make fields appear by default in high intensity and underlined, use the following assignment: $DEF_VIDEO BRI,UND Copy Related Links Video Attributes Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences. $fieldvideo Return or set the video attributes of the specified field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}